README for ATM-OCN-LND-MED NUOPC prototype
--------------------------------------

Dependencies:
  - ESMF v7.0.0 beta
  
Build:
  - Set environment variable ESMFMKFILE to point to the esmf.mk of your ESMF
    installation.
  - gmake
  
Execution:
  - Optionally set environment variable ESMF_RUNTIME_COMPLIANCECHECK to ON.
  - mpirun -np 8 ./esmApp
  
Output:
  - PET*.Log files containing compliance checker output if turned on.
  - The prototype outputs time stepping information to stdout.
  
Input: 
wget --no-check-certificate https://raw.githubusercontent.com/feiliuesmf/esmftest/master/xgrid/test2/corner_lat_0.5.nc
wget --no-check-certificate https://raw.githubusercontent.com/feiliuesmf/esmftest/master/xgrid/test2/corner_lon_0.5.nc
wget --no-check-certificate https://raw.githubusercontent.com/feiliuesmf/esmftest/master/xgrid/test2/center_lat_0.5.nc
wget --no-check-certificate https://raw.githubusercontent.com/feiliuesmf/esmftest/master/xgrid/test2/center_lon_0.5.nc
wget --no-check-certificate https://raw.githubusercontent.com/feiliuesmf/esmftest/master/xgrid/test2/mask_0.5.nc
wget --no-check-certificate https://raw.githubusercontent.com/feiliuesmf/esmftest/master/xgrid/test2/sst_0.5.nc
mkdir data
cd data
wget --no-check-certificate https://raw.githubusercontent.com/feiliuesmf/esmftest/master/xgrid/test1/ll1deg_grid.nc
